    "Due to their reliance on binarized concepts, concept bottleneck-based models generally require more computation [98].",
    "Another critical factor is the trade-off between the primary convolutional model and the interpretation method; the ideal explanation method should provide insights while sacrificing prediction accuracy to a minimum.",
